Package stringMatcher

The Package contains classes that methods to calculate different String similarity Metrics like Levenshtein's algorithm, Dice and Method to remove Stop words

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CompareDefination This algorithm is based on Dice Algorithm Reference: http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Algorithm_Implementation/Strings/Dice's_coefficient
CompareTerm This algorithm is based on Levenshtein's Algorithm References: http://en.wikibooks.org/wiki/Algorithm_Implementation/Strings/Levenshtein_distance
CompareTermDef This class is used to compare a Definition with a Term and return a score
RemoveStopWords This class is used for preprocess a string and removing all stop words from them
